      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible, mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! I've babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following the maintenance schedule. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. You won't find another one this clean! Feel free to reach out with any questions.",
