      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, presented in absolute showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and garage-kept since day one, the exterior boasts a mirror-like finish with zero chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh state, featuring premium leather that still carries that new-car scent and high-tech displays that function flawlessly. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete paper trail included. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car represents the pinnacle of its class. It drives as perfectly as it looks\u2014tight, responsive, and powerful. If you are looking for a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new, this is it.",
      "price": 48500.0,
